## text

### Source (en)

~~~text
In a table, the data items are arranged in columns. Is there a header for each of these describing what is in there?
~~~

### Translation (zh_Hant)

~~~text
在表格中，資料項目是以欄排列的。這些欄位是否各自都有一個標題說明欄位內是什麼？
~~~
